    "title": "Wasiwasi kwa Maskini",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wasiwasi kwa maskini",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu aliagiza Waisraeli kuwatunza watu wake kwa ajili ya ustawi wao. Agano la Waisraeli na Mungu ( Agano Maalum) pamoja na mtazamo wao wa kujiona kama familia kubwa ulisaidia kuzuia madai ya upendeleo. Familia inapaswa kusaidia wanachama wanaohitaji. Wanachama hawa walijumuisha wajane, yatima, maskini, na wageni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22\">Kutoka 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:10\">Mambo ya Walawi 19:10</a>).</p><p>Wakulima wanapaswa kuacha kingo za mashamba yao na mazao yaliyobaki kwa wale wanaohitaji (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">Mambo ya Walawi 23:22</a>). Watu maskini hawapaswi kunyonywa. Badala yake, wanapaswa kupewa mikopo bila riba, au mdaiwa anaweza kulipa deni kwa heshima kama mfanyakazi wa kuajiriwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:35-Lev25:42\">Mambo ya Walawi 25:35–42</a>). Hatua hizi zilihakikisha maskini wanapata chakula cha kula.</p><p>Biblia inaonyesha kujali maskini kwa kurekebisha mfumo wa sadaka kwa wale ambao hawawezi kumudu sadaka za gharama kubwa. Watu wangeweza kutumia ndege badala ya wana-kondoo kwa sadaka ya kuteketezwa kabisa na sadaka ya dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:14-Lev1:17\">Mambo ya Walawi 1:14–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:7-Lev5:10\">5:7–10</a>). Kulikuwa pia na marekebisho mengine katika sherehe za utakaso (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:21-Lev14:22\">14:21–22</a>). Mabadiliko yanayoonekana zaidi ni kuruhusu unga kama mbadala wa sadaka ya dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11-Lev5:13\">5:11–13</a>). Mabadiliko haya yalionyesha kuwa sadaka haikuashiria tena kutoa uhai kwa uhai. Hii ilifanywa kusaidia watu ambao hawawezi kumudu wanyama. Inaonyesha wazi tamaa ya Mungu kwa maskini kupata msamaha wa dhambi hata kama hawawezi kumudu mwana-kondoo.</p><p>Mada hii inashughulikia wasiwasi wa manabii kuhusu maskini na wasiojiweza. Walitoa wito wa haki ya kijamii na huruma (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">Isaya 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6\">Amosi 2:6</a>). Manabii walizungumza kwa nguvu dhidi ya wale waliowakandamiza wahitaji (tazama kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1-Amos4:3\">Amosi 4:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:8\">Amosi 8:4–8</a>). Mungu hakukubali ibada za watu zilizokuwa na taratibu nyingi ikiwa walikuwa na hatia ya ukosefu wa haki na ukandamizaji kwa wakati huo huo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15-Isa1:20\">Isaya 1:15–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">Mika 6:6–8</a>).</p><p>Mitazamo na matendo sahihi kuelekea Mungu na wengine ni muhimu zaidi kuliko sherehe za ibada. Wazo hili linaonekana katika hadithi za injili kuhusu sadaka ya mjane maskini. Yesu anasifu sadaka yake si kwa thamani yake ya kifedha, bali kwa ibada inayoonyesha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">Marko 12:41–44</a>). Matendo ya kidini yanaweza hata kuzuia msaada kwa wale wanaohitaji (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:9-Mark7:13\">Marko 7:9–13</a>).</p><p>Yesu na kanisa la awali walionyesha kujali kwa maskini. Yesu alisema kuwa misheni yake ilijumuisha kuleta matumaini kwa maskini na kuwaweka huru waliokandamizwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:16-Luke4:21\">Luka 4:16–21</a>). Aliwaonya dhidi ya kupuuza maskini (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:31\">Luka 16:19–31</a>). Alisema kusaidia maskini ilikuwa muhimu kwa wafuasi wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:23\">Luka 18:18–23</a>). Kufuatia mafundisho ya Kristo, kanisa la awali lilihakikisha kuwajali wale wenye mahitaji (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">Matendo 2:44–45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">Matendo 4:32–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:3-1Tim5:16\">1 Timotheo 5:3–16</a>). Kama manabii, waliamini kuwa kuwatendea watu wa chini vibaya kulifanya mazoea ya kidini kuwa yasiyo na maana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:17-1Cor11:29\">1 Wakorintho 11:17–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27-Jas2:17\">Yakobo 1:27–2:17</a>).</p><p>Mungu anawajali maskini, mada inayopatikana katika Maandiko yote. Wakristo wanapaswa kuwa na mtazamo huu kwa wale wanaohitaji.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22-Exod22:27\">Kutoka 22:22–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:6-Exod23:11\">23:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:7\">Mambo ya Walawi 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11\">11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:21-Lev14:22\">14:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">19:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:22\">23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17-Deut10:19\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 10:17–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:4-Deut15:11\">15:4–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:9-Deut16:12\">16:9–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:6-Deut24:22\">24:6–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:12-Deut26:13\">26:12–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:17-Deut27:19\">27:17–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1 Samweli 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:13-Ps10:18\">Zaburi 10:13–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:10\">35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5\">68:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">Mithali 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15-Isa1:17\">Isaya 1:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6\">Amosi 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1\">4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:7\">8:4–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">Mika 6:6–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">Marko 12:41–44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20\">Luka 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">14:12–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:17\">Yakobo 2:1–17</a></p>",
